OL,3,CPost Office 'Capture' cases head to
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FThe first convictions based on the
OL,7,FPost Office Capture accounting
OL,8,Fsoftware, which the organisation used
OL,9,Fbefore the faulty Horizon system, have
OL,10,Fbeen referred to the Court of Appeal.
OL,12,FThe case of Patricia Owen, who was
OL,13,Ffound guilty of five counts of theft
OL,14,Fin June 1998, had been lined up to be
OL,15,Freferred in July and the Criminal
OL,16,FCases Review Commission (CCRC)
OL,17,Fconfirmed the referral on Thursday.
