OL,6,FMrs Owen pleaded not guilty to all
OL,7,Ffive charges after the Broad Oak Post
OL,8,FOffice branch in Sweechgate,
OL,9,FCanterbury, was left with a shortfall
OL,10,Fof #6,000.
OL,12,FThe CCRC said it is now up to the
OL,13,FCourt of Appeal whether her
OL,14,Fconvictions are unsafe and should be
OL,15,Fquashed.
OL,17,FMrs Owens died in 2003 but her family
OL,18,Fhas carried on the fight to clear her
OL,19,Fname.
